article_id:869,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing the Next Summon Showcase, Madcap Misfits!,image_path:,message:<div>The next Summon Showcase, Madcap Misfits, kicks off <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1573624800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>Appearance rates for featured adventurers and dragons will be boosted during this showcase!</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for featured summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1573624800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1574920740"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the featured adventurers and dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div><div class="summonPickUp">
<div class="imageStatusWrap">
