			<div class="status">
				<div class="title">Adventurer Details</div>
				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>A sylvan girl obsessed with Luca (or "Luccy").<br>She sticks to him like a shadow, and doesn't<br>seem to know when to stop. That can all be<br>quite tiresome, but she must have a good<br>reason, right?</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div></div><div class="skill explanation">
	<div class="title">Skills</div>
	<dl>
			<dt>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/675c04a4767e3334ef726465460e4be62.png"></span>
				<span>Love's Liberation</span>
			</dt>
			<dd>
				<div>
					Deals flame damage to the target.
				</div>
			</dd>
	
			<dt>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/4a7025c31c5d89c3fa80184027f3d2172.png"></span>
				<span>Bruiser Bliss</span>
			</dt>
			<dd>
				<div>
					Activates "Obsession" for 60 seconds.<br>During Obsession, the user's strength is<br>increased by 30%, and they will take damage<br>equal to 3% of their maximum HP every<br>time they attack or use a skill. Furthermore, their HP<br>will be restored by 5% of the damage inflicted by<br>Love's Liberation, up to a maximum of 49%<br>of the user's maximum HP. The effects of<br>Obsession will be removed upon shapeshifting.
				</div>
			</dd>
	</dl></div><div class="exAbility explanation">
	<div class="title">Co-abilities</div>
	<dl>
			<dt>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b2f1d14494e80343f38734ca9a2b72842.png"></span>
				<span>Skill Haste +15%</span>
			</dt>
			<dd>
				<div>
					Increases skill gauge fill rate by 15%.<br>Benefits your whole team.
				</div>
			</dd>
	</dl></div><div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/8c8841b3f5aa35fb71f07f9075152dba2.png"></span><span>HP Below 30% = Strength & Attack Rate III</span></dt><dd><div>Increases strength by 20% and attack rate by 10%<br>when HP is 30% or below.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/e23fa30b574bf7f565547e4d26946c1f2.png"></span><span>Stun Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to stun by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/94180caecbefc8ce72737608068138b12.png"></span><span>Obsessive Love II</span></dt><dd><div>When the "Obsession" effect is active,<br>increases strength by 30%, and decreases<br>defense by 20%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities, and represent the adventurer at maximum level with all mana circles unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured dragon:</div><div><div class="summonPickUp">
<div class="imageStatusWrap">
