					</li>
					<li class="atk">
						<span>Strength</span>
						<span>127</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="total">
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png" alt=""></span>
				<span>991</span>
			</div>
		</div>
			<div class="status">
				<div class="title">Dragon Details</div>
				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>A fiery dragon from southern Hinomoto. <br>Born in a volcano, his flame-hardened body<br>renders all but the most powerful attacks null.<br>If you meet him off the battlefield, he will likely<br>treat you to his homeland's famous fried chicken.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div></div><div class="skill explanation">
	<div class="title">Skills</div>
	<dl>
			<dt>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/120e337b87db017cf609bde65d5268d72.png"></span>
				<span>Coruscating Flames</span>
			</dt>
			<dd>
				<div>
					Deals flame damage to surrounding enemies,<br>and inflicts burn.
				</div>
			</dd>
	</dl></div><div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png"></span><span>(Flame) Strength +45%</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Flame: <br>increases strength by 45%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png"></span><span>(Flame) Primed Strength +15%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases the strength of the adventurer you<br>are currently controlling by 15% for 10 seconds<br>every time their initial skill, displayed at the<br>top of their skill list, becomes available for use,<br>providing they are flame-attuned. After activating,<br>this ability will not activate again for 15 seconds.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>The stats shown here represent the dragon at maximum level, maximum bond, and fully unbound. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. For information about featured adventurers and dragons, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1573538400,update_time1573439350